      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 2
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make and bake the biscuits, 12 to 14 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Preheat the oven to 175°C fan. Pulse together the {{plain-flour}} for the biscuit, {{cocoa-powder}} for the biscuit, {{icing-sugar}} for the biscuit, and {{sea-salt-fine}} in a bowl. Rub in the cold {{unsalted-butter}} for the biscuit until the mixture resembles fine crumbs. Add the {{golden-syrup}} and mix until the dough comes together, adding a splash of {{whole-milk}} for the biscuit if needed. Roll to 3 mm thick on a lightly floured surface and cut into rectangles of about 7 x 3 cm. Place on lined baking trays and prick each one with a fork a few times. Bake for 12 to 14 minutes, rotating the tray at 7 minutes. Cool completely on the tray. They will crisp as they cool.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the filling and sandwich",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Beat the {{unsalted-butter}} for the filling until pale. Beat in the sifted {{icing-sugar}} for the filling and {{cocoa-powder}} for the filling until smooth. Add {{whole-milk}} for the filling to reach a spreadable consistency. To make a ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "sandwich biscuit",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp9yth8t0000i4v4rz6k2g2h"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": ": spread a teaspoon of filling on the flat side of one biscuit and press a second biscuit on top, flat side down. Press firmly. Leave to set for 20 minutes before eating.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
